  "notes": "Great-grandfather on the Burgess line. Born in Virginia. Father Benjamin Franklin Burgess (1845-1894) died Dec 14, 1894 in DC. Brother: Walter N. Burgess (1878-1977). Married Amelia Bertha Recker on October 26, 1898 in Alexandria, VA. Four children: Brainard Recker Burgess (1899-1950), Alton Edwin Burgess (1904-1970), Flora Esther Burgess (1907-1996), Roy Wilson Burgess (1918-2006). Traveled to Key West, FL in Feb 1925. Died December 16, 1944 at age 69 in Washington DC. Buried in Suitland, MD."
